{"tid":2263068,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[成績表]豐樹北亞上半年總收入跌一成 又一城租戶獲約1.98億元租金減免","createTime":"2020-10-29T14:55:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-30T05:19:12.000Z","uid":51271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a687ab340513bdba5731628473de3a27c83214fd","tid":2263068,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T14:55:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1603978211965&amp;issue=20201029\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpfinance.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1603978211965%26issue%3D20201029&d=L3LYojiCq%2FWCCnzMgLa5KExj1a1M9JfR6d2dSWReNkw%3D&h=9895b752\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1603978211965&amp;issue=20201029</a><br />\n<br />\n持有又一城的豐樹北亞商業信託（Mapletree North Asia Commercial Trust）公布今年4月至9月底的上半年業績，總收入按年下跌9.6%至1.9億新加坡元，淨物業收入按年下跌17.7%至1.397億新加坡元。集團表示，跌幅主要受疫情影響，又一城及北京佳程廣場平均租金下跌，前者租戶獲得3490萬新加坡元（約1.98億港元）租金減免。<br />\n<br />\n截至今年9月底止，又一城商場零售續租租金下跌12%，出租率為99%。又一城上半年總收入及淨物業收入分別下跌32.6%及38.9%，跌幅主要來自租金減免及較低的零售租金，不過港元兌新加坡元匯率上升抵消了部分影響。集團指出，又一城租戶的銷售及人流按年下跌36.2%及45.5%，主要是社交距離措施及餐飲限制所影響。<br />\n<br />\n豐樹北亞商業信託預計，香港疫情將繼續對零售業帶來沉重壓力，由於職位空缺增加，短期內零售租金將保持下降趨勢，大部分零售商將維持審慎態度，零售開始復蘇才會長租。集團又指，雖然入境旅客不太可能復蘇，但疫情轉趨穩定，本地消費情緒或會進一步改善。由於零售業疲軟，集團預計又一城平均續租或重新出租租金將在下半年繼續下跌，將據疫情對租戶影響，繼續提供租金減免措施。"},{"pid":"4024fcb5685a3722554c8b64a84806b7d982410c","tid":2263068,"uid":3086,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T15:01:05.000Z","msg":"唔知今年有無聖誕樹睇呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef3ea90bee70fb4fcf9343fe77e1633a23480424","tid":2263068,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4024fcb5685a3722554c8b64a84806b7d982410c","tid":2263068,"uid":3086,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T15:01:05.000Z","msg":"唔知今年有無聖誕樹睇呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T23:14:31.000Z","msg":"唔敢放咁高"},{"pid":"87988166a77d549c3b305a0ce2c9457a5345c3d5","tid":2263068,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T23:42:19.000Z","msg":"又一城不了 自從比太古賣左之後爛場一個"},{"pid":"de8614eb3ab964a704477c758cf146cbd141575d","tid":2263068,"uid":2054,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T23:45:35.000Z","msg":"又一城教材式裝修<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7135b1c9e781a98210b94b00e9e5a5eca4303a5","tid":2263068,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef3ea90bee70fb4fcf9343fe77e1633a23480424","tid":2263068,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4024fcb5685a3722554c8b64a84806b7d982410c","tid":2263068,"uid":3086,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T15:01:05.000Z","msg":"唔知今年有無聖誕樹睇呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T23:14:31.000Z","msg":"唔敢放咁高"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T23:47:53.000Z","msg":"有國安法唔怕 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/03.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08bd92b1a5712ead6e852981e567e2975633349c","tid":2263068,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T05:19:12.000Z","msg":"成績表<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}